  "description": {
    "zh": "你造的枪绝对惊人，至少我的哥们Victor是这么说的，我想我可以信任他。\n\n在他真正部署他的人在塔科夫之前，他想知道更多事情——特别是检查他们的装备表现如何，他们主要使用俄罗斯装备，显然……9x21枪，你造的那些，NPP KlASS装备，这里那里的一些高切头盔，你知道。总之，他想在你们找到三个走私者藏身处的区域试试它们，你觉得你能做到吗？你当然能，做完就回来。\n\n指定装备：\n - SR-2M Veresk 9x21冲锋枪 或 Serdyukov SR-1MP Gyurza 9x21手枪\n - 任何NPP KlASS防弹衣或胸挂\n - NPP KlASS Tor-2头盔、LShZ轻量化头盔或任何Ops-Core头盔",
    "en": "The guns you built were absolutely amazing, that's what my guy Victor said at least, I think I can trust him.\n\nHe wants to know about a few more things before he actually deploys his men in Tarkov - Specifically check on how their gear performs, they run mostly russian gear, obviously... 9x21 guns, the ones you built, NPP KlASS equipment, high-cut helmets here and there, you know. Anyway, he wants to try them out in the zones where you found the hideouts of the three smugglers, you think you can do that? Of course you can, come back when it's done.\n\nSpecified Gear :\n - SR-2M Veresk 9x21 Submachine Gun or Serdyukov SR-1MP Gyurza 9x21 Pistol\n - Any NPP KlASS Bodyarmor or Platecarrier\n - NPP KlASS Tor-2 Helmet, LShZ Lightweight Helmet or any Ops-Core Helmet"
  },
